    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-6">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
      BackyardSaunaPro.com participates in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.
    </p>
    <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
      When you click on product links on this site and make a purchase, we may receive a small commission at no additional cost to you. This helps us keep the site running and the content free.
    </p>
    <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
      We also participate in other affiliate programs. All affiliate relationships are disclosed where relevant.
    </p>
    <p class="text-stone-600">
      Our editorial opinions are independent of our affiliate relationships. We only recommend products we believe provide genuine value.
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>
